---
import Layout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import SinglePost from '~/components/blog/SinglePost.astro';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import rawDumpToolImage from '~/assets/images/raw-dump-tool.jpeg';
import rawDumpToolImage2 from '~/assets/images/raw-dump-tool-security.png';
import Button from '~/components/ui/Button.astro';
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';

const metadata = {
  title: 'Raw Dump Tool - Memory Dumping Forensics Tool',
  description:
    'A Python-based GUI Memory Dumping Forensics Tool for digital investigators, featuring encryption, tamper detection, and comprehensive analysis capabilities.',
  pubDate: new Date('2025-04-29'),
};

const post = {
  id: 'raw-dump-tool',
  slug: 'raw-dump-tool',
  permalink: '/projects/raw-dump-tool',
  title: metadata.title,
  description: metadata.description,
  publishDate: metadata.pubDate,
  image: rawDumpToolImage,
  github: 'https://github.com/neerajlovecyber/raw-dump-tool',
};
---

<Layout metadata={metadata}>
  <SinglePost post={post} url={post.permalink}>
    <div class="prose dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Raw Dump Tool</h1>

      <p class="lead mb-8">
        In the realm of digital forensics, the ability to extract and analyze volatile memory (RAM) contents is
        paramount. Raw Dump Tool is a Python-based Graphical User Interface (GUI) Memory Dumping Forensics Tool,
        designed to streamline the process of memory extraction, analysis, and data security.
      </p>

      <h2>Features that Empower</h2>

      <h3>Dump File Encryption & Decryption</h3>
      <p>
        One of the standout features is its ability to not only extract volatile memory but also encrypt the resulting
        memory dump file. This encryption ensures that sensitive data collected from the target system remains
        protected, accessible only to authorized individuals.
      </p>

      <h3>Dump File Tamper Detection</h3>
      <p>
        Maintaining the integrity and authenticity of collected evidence is crucial. The tool incorporates tamper
        detection mechanisms designed to identify any unauthorized alterations to the memory dump file.
      </p>

      <div class="my-8">
        <Image src={rawDumpToolImage} alt="Raw Dump Tool Demo" class="rounded-lg shadow-lg" width={800} height={450} />
        <Image src={rawDumpToolImage2} alt="Raw Dump Tool Demo" class="rounded-lg shadow-lg" width={800} height={450} />
      </div>

      <h2>Getting Started</h2>
      <ol>
        <li><strong>Clone the Repository:</strong> Find the Raw Dump Tool on GitHub</li>
        <li>
          <strong>Run the Executable:</strong> Execute the provided executable file (requires internet connection)
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Configure Options:</strong> Choose appropriate options for memory dumping, encryption, and decryption
        </li>
        <li><strong>Start the Dumping Process:</strong> Initiate through the user-friendly interface</li>
        <li><strong>Analyze the Dump:</strong> Tool automatically analyzes memory contents</li>
        <li><strong>Encryption (Optional):</strong> Specify encryption key for additional security</li>
        <li><strong>Begin Analysis:</strong> Start your digital forensics investigation</li>
      </ol>

      <h2>Join the Community</h2>
      <p>Your contributions are highly appreciated! You can help improve the tool through:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Bug Reports</li>
        <li>Feature Requests</li>
        <li>Pull Requests</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Licensing</h2>
      <p>
        The Raw Dump Tool is licensed under the MIT License, allowing you the freedom to modify and distribute while
        adhering to the license terms.
      </p>

      <div class="bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 p-8 rounded-lg">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Get in Touch</h2>
        <p>Have questions or suggestions? Reach out to Neeraj Singh:</p>
        <ul class="">
          <li>
            Email: <a href="mailto:neerajlovecyber@gmail.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800"
              >neerajlovecyber@gmail.com</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            LinkedIn: <a
              href="https://linkedin.com/in/neerajlovecyber"
              class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer">Connect on LinkedIn</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            GitHub: <a
              href="https://github.com/neerajlovecyber/raw-dump-tool"
              class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer">View Project Repository</a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-8 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 p-8 rounded-lg text-center">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-800 dark:text-white">
          Ready to enhance your digital forensics toolkit?
        </h3>
        <p class="text-lg mb-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
          Download Raw Dump Tool now and streamline your memory analysis workflows!
        </p>
        <Button
          variant="primary"
          href="https://github.com/neerajlovecyber/RawDumpTool"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="text-xl"
        >
          <Icon name="tabler:download" class="w-6 h-6 mr-2" />
          Download Raw Dump Tool
        </Button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </SinglePost>
</Layout>
